flowchart TD
    A[Browser] -->|WebSocket| B[Node / TypeScript Gateway]

    B --> B1[Serves Frontend]
    B --> B2[Receives Browser Messages]
    B -->|Forwards audio/text jobs| C[Python Worker]
    C --> C1[OpenAI Transcription]
    C --> C2[OpenAI LLM Response]
    C --> C3[OpenAI TTS]

    C -->|Returns transcript / text / audio| B
    B -->|Returns transcript / text / audio| A
